{"tid":2298454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呂智恆阻清理連儂牆案　裁判官陳炳宙怒屌律政司食環署「濫用司法程序，令司法蒙上污點」","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T04:38:54.000Z","uid":6497,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"451aba3f036fc79c06bca3f65aea26bcddcfca57","tid":2298454,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201124/s00001/1606192401381/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201124%2Fs00001%2F1606192401381%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=46301071\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201124%2Fs00001%2F1606192401381%2F&h=4b968811\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201124/s00001/1606192401381/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201124/s00001/b53ebfd3e528ba3b56cb0d4105d1ad76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201124%2Fs00001%2Fb53ebfd3e528ba3b56cb0d4105d1ad76.jpg&h=e5d85fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食環署工人去年11月在粉嶺港鐵站對出的天橋清理，社工呂智恆被指阻礙一名食環署督察清理，今（24日）在粉嶺裁判法院被裁定一項阻礙公職人員執行公務罪不成立，兼得訟費。裁判官陳炳宙表示，<span class=\"red\">事主當時身穿便服，沒有出示委任證，是故意隱瞞公職人員身分，令被告進入圈套，批評控方依賴不光彩的證據將被告定罪，「濫用司法程序，令司法蒙上污點」。</span><br />\n<br />\n呂智恆（38歲）原被控於去年11月23日在粉嶺港鐵站的天橋上，阻礙食環署一級督察麥慶安執行公務。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">陳官裁決指出，麥慶安作供時聲稱已交代身分及行動詳情，但片段顯示被告多次追問麥慶安的身分，麥慶安拒絕作答，一直走來走去迴避被告，認為其作供不可信。<br />\n<br />\n陳官稱，麥慶安當時身穿便服，必須表明身分及出示委任證，但他沒有這樣做，顯然是故意隱瞞公職人員的身分，誤導被告他只是食環署的外判人員。陳官認為，這種誤解已成為被告的合理抗辯理由，加上案發時清理行動仍未開始，被告的行為不構成阻礙，裁定他罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n陳官批評，麥慶安的行為嚴重不恰當，但控方卻依賴其證供，做法有違公義，直斥控方「依賴啲咁唔光彩嘅證據將被告定罪，是濫用司法程序，令司法蒙上污點」。辯方申請訟費，遭控方反對，但陳官認為控方是次起訴的決定不合理，最終批出訟費。</span>"},{"pid":"1980fe5d7b645d6bde51dbeed1bc8af6114f3d86","tid":2298454,"uid":6497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"連陳炳宙都頂佢地唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8198a544ed99b019270ce9514ed52e3386c9a169","tid":2298454,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e365ad995792df58a7f502dfb6a676126c63dc7","tid":2298454,"uid":293539,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"做得公務員都係狗黎架啦"},{"pid":"602da075e9551a3ad520bcd10a0a2d0ec4c826b9","tid":2298454,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228430e514dec16f9c873c8d1e5016a5e409f980","tid":2298454,"uid":175194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e365ad995792df58a7f502dfb6a676126c63dc7","tid":2298454,"uid":293539,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"做得公務員都係狗黎架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n加入共產黨唔通係黃咩"},{"pid":"85353148b0913ca6a0daa487e7fd2223f3281f0b","tid":2298454,"uid":6942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"告返控方啦屌佢老母"},{"pid":"ee27222a826d0bf004f2b21c89c67178bc15d1fc","tid":2298454,"uid":34457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"屌你食環狗當自己警狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n使唔使比枝鎗你陀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318f40a4398bba078faf9e5f243afb625baae1b5","tid":2298454,"uid":135274,"like":6,"di